OL,3,CSpaxton village 'dreadfully upset'
OL,4,Cafter scarecrows vandalised
OL,6,FResidents in Spaxton near Bridgwater
OL,7,Fare scrambling to repair more than a
OL,8,Fdozen scarecrows that were vandalised
OL,9,Fahead of their annual village show.
OL,11,FAccording to police, it appears the 20
OL,12,Fhomemade scarecrows in the village
OL,13,Fwere driven over by a car overnight.
OL,15,FResidents say children were left in
OL,16,Ftears after the incident but the
OL,17,Fcommunity is determined to carry out
OL,18,Fthe weekend's flower show as planned.
