OL,3,CSpaxton village 'dreadfully upset'
OL,4,Cafter scarecrows vandalised
OL,6,FVicky Hemming, the chair of Spaxton
OL,7,FFlower Show, explained: "Everybody was
OL,8,Fdreadfully upset but actually the
OL,9,Freally heartening point was that
OL,10,Fpeople came, we had a working party on
OL,11,Fthe Wednesday night, about 30 people
OL,12,Farrived and we pieced everything back
OL,13,Ftogether as best we could."
OL,15,FResident Ali Bond said: "The children
OL,16,Fwere so upset."
OL,18,FShe added: "Children often walk along
OL,19,Fhere to school in the morning and they
OL,20,Fsaw everything strewn all over the
OL,21,Ffloor, all their hard work."
