OL,3,CSpaxton village 'dreadfully upset'
OL,4,Cafter scarecrows vandalised
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said: "We
OL,7,Freceived a 101 call to a report of
OL,8,Fcriminal damage relating to 20
OL,9,Fscarecrows, which were created as part
OL,10,Fof a village competition, at about
OL,11,F3.10pm on Wednesday 23 July.
OL,13,F"The scarecrows were placed along both
OL,14,Fsides of a road, and it appears a car
OL,15,Fhas been used to drive over them.
OL,17,F"We believe the incident was carried
OL,18,Fout by somebody outside the village
OL,19,Fbetween 11.30pm on Tuesday 22 July and
OL,20,F6.30am on Wednesday 23 July.
